snippet.title: PENTAKILL - Mortal Reminder (Full Band Cover)
snippet.description:
Fellow Armsmen!

This is Pentakill - Mortal Reminder

I am back with a great collaboration with amazing musicians from around the world. Though it took longer than I hoped for to have them in this project because of their booked schedules, I am very satisfied with the result and hope you enjoy this one as well!

Thank you to Riot Games, League of Legends we love your work and the music you have created so much!

It's been our intentions to make this cover an individual thing and not a direct copy of the original. It's up to you to decide whether the attempt has been successful or not. Please, visit our channels below and don't forget to like it and subscribe the channel for more videos.



Siegfried Song (Symmetric Chaos, South Korea) - Lead Vocals, Harmony Vocals, Video Editing
Leo Pe単a (Jotun Studio, Spain) - Rhythm Guitars, Mixing, Mastering, Video Editing
Alex Nasla (Symmetric Chaos, USA) - Keyboards and Orchestration
Jonny Sobrino (Jotun Studio, Spain) - Bass Guitars
Patrick Fallang (Symmetric Chaos, Norway) - Lead Guitars
Dirk Verbeuren (Megadeth, Belgium) - Drums 

[Siegfried Song]
